PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Public Works and Government Services of TERRI M. LENKE, of Saskatoon, Saskatchewan, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Canada Post Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of two years, in the place of Richard William Nerysoo, whose term has expired.
